## Technical Details

### PLATO Tile Schema (Final Version)
```json
{
  "id": "unique_identifier",
  "domain": "knowledge_domain",
  "question": "technical_question",
  "answer": "comprehensive_answer",
  "prerequisites": ["tile_id_1", "tile_id_2"],
  "related_tiles": ["tile_id_3", "tile_id_4"],
  "difficulty": "beginner|intermediate|advanced",
  "tags": ["tag1", "tag2", "tag3"],
  "code_example": "inline_code_snippet",
  "next_steps": ["tile_id_5", "tile_id_6"],
  "rating": {
    "quality": "1-5",
    "clarity": "1-5",
    "depth": "1-5"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_8601"
}
```

### Fleet Knowledge Base Architecture
```
fleet-knowledge/
├── plato-tiles/           # 1805 tiles organized by domain
├── indexes/                 # Full-text search index, domain mappings
├── pathways/               # Learning sequences, prerequisite chains
├── concepts/               # Concept graph, cross-references
├── frontends/              # 4 enhanced HTML applications
└── metadata/               # Tile metadata, ratings, statistics
```

